{"title":"采茶姑娘回村庄","authors":["徐锁"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":6,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"采茶姑娘回村庄"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐锁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"含笑的太阳落山岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采茶的姑娘回村庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"下山就像那下楼梯呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路说笑一路唱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑姑娘说茶叶儿壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巧姑娘夸茶十里香；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翠姑娘赞茶卖钱多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都添花衣裳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大姐本不爱讲话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忍不住那喜悦也开腔："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茶好别忘了咱的党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有那战士守边疆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱把嫩叶选两筐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送给北京送边疆；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山高水长表心意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们意见怎么样？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姑娘们都夸好主张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福的歌儿飞远方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采茶的姑娘下了山呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"食堂的钟声响叮当……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}